caption.text: I'm actually not a fan of the touch controls in this new Mario Kart mobile game, but I guess I'm playing it anyway because somewhere out there is a kid--and this kid is pretty good at Mario Kart, but all his friends want to play are FIFA, Madden and Call of Duty, so he jumps online to show the world that he may not shine at the more popular stuff everybody else wants to play, but damnit, he can do wonders with a red shell. So, maybe I'm not really enjoying this one, but I play because as someone who was there, I feel a responsibility for that kid. Mostly because he needs to know that I'm out here somewhere, telling him to go practice FIFA because to be the man, you've gotta *beat* the man, I've been the best there is, the best there was and the best there ever will be since 19 fucking 92 and I'm sure as hell NOT STEPPING ASIDE NOW. WHOOOOOOO!! #empoweringmessages

Level-5 has changed the title of the Inazuma Eleven Ares game to Inazuma Eleven: Great Road of Heroes and announced a spring 2020 release window for Japan.
.
In a blog post, Level-5 apologized for the miscalculations that have occurred in development thus far, which resulted in the Inazuma Eleven Ares anime series and its sequel Inazuma Eleven: Orion no Kokuin to conclude before the release of the game. However, development of the game has since moved from an outsourced to a fully in-house development system, which has allowed further system revisions to create a game with more exciting battles.
.
Inazuma Eleven: Great Road of Heroes is based on the drama of Inazuma Eleven Ares and features additional episodes in which past characters also appear.
.
Like previous Inazuma Eleven titles, the game system will offer a high level of freedom in which player positions are indicated by the controller (or mouse). It promises to be a completely new type of RPG that incorporates eSports developments, as well as enhanced hack-and-slash elements such as battles and player gatherings. Level-5 also hopes to make a deep online system with a wide range of tactics in whch national tournaments can be held.
.
Inazuma Eleven: Great Road of Heroes is in development for PlayStation 4, Switch, iOS, and Android.
.

🤓Pokémon Épée / Bouclier : Un stream de 24h pour admirer la forêt de Glimwood Tangle🤓
.
En effet, plutôt que de faire intervenir les producteurs du jeu comme c'est souvent le cas dans ce genre de diffusion, le studio a décidé de "filmer" la forêt de Glimwood Tangle durant 24h. Ce lieu situé au cœur de la région Galar abrite de nombreux Pokémon que nous pourrons observer dans leur habitant naturel au fil des heures. Pour découvrir tout ça, il faudra donc se rendre sur Twitch, YouTube ou NicoNico le 4 octobre à partir de 15h (heure française).

caption.text:
Sooo da melde ich mich auch mal wieder zurück mit meinen last pickups🙈 alle 3 Spiele habe ich mir heute gekauft, auf Links Awakening war ich sehr hyped da TLoZ einfach meine liebste Spielereihe ist und ich Links Awakening immer sehr interessant fand, es jedoch nie spielen konnte👎🏽 deswegen bin ich umso gehypter
Dragon Quest XI ist mein allererstes Dragon Quest und es sah in den Teasern sehr cool aus und der Held hat bei Smash auch einen sehr positiven Eindruck hinterlassen🍭
Zu guter letzt Daemon X Machina, ein Spiel wo ich nicht weiß mit welchen Erwartungen ich rangehen soll, mich persönlich hat es von den Teasern her mehr angesprochen als Astral Chain, die Grafik sah sehr cool aus und mit Robotern kann ich mich auch anfreunden, zudem hat mir ein netter Mann im Saturn geraten dieses Spiel mitzunehmen da er selber sehr begeistert war.🤖
Alles in allem bin ich sehr gespannt wie mir die 3 Spiele gefallen werden!😊

caption.text:
Anunciados nuevos mandos de #8BitDo para #NintendoSwitchLite

Nos llega un curioso anuncio procedente de 8BitDo, a quien seguramente conocen por ser una compañía que en el pasado ha creado fantásticos mandos para #NintendoSwitch. Pues bien, recientemente ha desvelado nuevos controladores para Nintendo Switch Lite.

De acuerdo con lo compartido, se trata de un mando «ultraportátil», perfecto para juegos en #2D. Estas son sus características: • Funcionalidad completa con #Switch: todos los botones principales son compatibles
• Compatible con Switch, #Windows, #macOS, #Android y más
• Batería recargable de iones de litio
• USB-C
• Diseño portátil plano para que puedas llevarlo a donde quieras

Si estás interesado, ya puedes reservarlo en Amazon por 24,99$. Se lanzará el 30 de octubre. .
.

RING FIT ADVENTURE, GAME KESEHATAN TERBARU DARI NINTENDO

Nintendo kembali menampilkan game unik, yang mengharuskan pemain berolahraga untuk menyelesaikan permainan! Hadir dengan judul Ring Fit Adventure, game ini bakal mengubah latihan yang gamer lakukan lewat Ring-Con dan Leg Strap, menjadi movement dan aksi bagi karakter utamamu. Ring Fit Adventure (juga Ring-Con dan Leg Strap) bakal dirilis tanggal 18 Oktober dengan banderol harga $79.99.

preview_comments.text: @the_fuckn_cosmo gliscor made it to being a top tier mon with an awesome ability where if it's poisoned it'll heal a little. Gallade was a male/physical attacker counterpart to Gardevoir, it's literally an option so I have no clue how this ruined an evolutionary line in any way. Okay Electabuzz is just garbage, I doubt anyone used it on a team over other electric types. Electivire at least gave Electabuzz another chance to be relevant.

@globglogabgalab it wasn't about how "viable" they are, at least not to me. I mean hell, the design for electivire just looked horrible in my eyes. It didn't fit with the evolution line whatsoever, Gallade was good to have, so that I disagree with. Also, Rhyperior? It was an evolution no one really needed all too much. At the time it was used more frequently, but over shadowed by other pokemon that better fit it's role on most competitive teams. PorygonZ as well, I hardly ever see anyone use it, let alone acknowledge it. The design really didn't appeal, it didn't need a third evolution (the only good that came from it is the eviolite for porygon 2, which says so much more about it's final evolution)

É melhor comprar outro jogo ou juntar mais um pouco e comprar o wireless. Um sonho para quem é altx e tem a mão grande e um pesadelo para quem é pequenininhx. Ele é mais robusto, cansa menos a mão, mais leve e é lindo. No entanto ele não tem uma das funções principais que é o sensor de movimento e o rumble, então, a depender do que você vai jogar fica impossível ou quase isso. Em todo caso se você se apaixonou e continua muito querendo um mesmo assim tenta no Mercado Livre, lá é muito mais em conta do que comprar em loja de shopping. #nintendoswitchgames #nintendoswitch #breathofthewild #transboynerd #thelegendofzelda #botw #lgbtgeeks #lgbtnerds #zelda #nintendolife #nintendobrasil

caption.text:
Another review! Let’s go❤️! Mario kart tour in the house🥳! Let’s do this!⁣
⁣
So Mario kart tour is now out on iOS 🍎 and Android 👽! And I like it on my perspective so let’s gooooo🔥!⁣ ⁣
🌎 Graphics: This is the best part of the game! For a mobile game is this looking gorgeous! You have also a battery saver and it makes the graphics bad and I mean really bad😑! But the graphics are overall really good❤️! ⁣
⁣
🎮 Gameplay: The drifting is really clunky... like I needed to practice 3 hours to get comfortable with it😐.. I don’t like the controls! And the normal settings (without drifting) is really slow and stuff 🐢... i don’t just don’t like it...
⁣
🎼 Music: The Music is the same like all the other Mario kart games... but that don’t means that it isn’t good!😁 I like Mario kart music and it is just good but maybe they can add one new song or something🙃! The Music is not bad!⁣
⁣
❓Others: Micro-transactions...🤮⁣
This is what I personally hate of mobile games! For example: The Gold pass is 6 Dollars a month😤! That is 72 dollars a year😨! For a fricking mobile game! A MOBILE GAME!!! And what do you get? GOLDEN STICKERS! Wtf!!! This is what I hate the most🤬!⁣
⁣
📈 Score: Graphics = 8,4 ⁣  Gameplay = 6,5⁣  Music =  7,2⁣  Others. = 3,1⁣
⁣ = 6,3⁣
⁣
Maybe you have other thoughts and let me know that🙃! maybe I change my mind😋!⁣
⁣
